quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  26,111,Anninnal koo nummasnaah koo katatnaah sinaamak boola-le mari koo kataate way? Kaak iyyen kay mari
  26,112,"Nabii Nuuc:usun abak sugen taamoomih ixxiga mayyu, cagalah anu ken kah seecam iimaanâ kalah keenik iyye"
  26,113,"Ken cisab kee galtò numul matan yi-Rabbiy qellittem yaaxigel tan tet akke waytek, woh aaxiginnitoonuy amah axcuk mananniton"
  26,114,Kaadu anu yi-seecol yeemene mara xiiriya num hinniyo
  26,115,"Anu abbay sinam xiiriya hinniyo, baxxaqqa iyya meesiisey Yallih digaalak sin meesiisa akke waytek"
  26,116,Nuucow ama seecok aadeewaytek xeetit qiden marak numuk teyna akketto kaak iyyen
  26,117,"Too waqdi Nabii Nuuc isi Rabbi seeceeh:yi-Rabbow diggah yi- mari yoo dirabboyseh iyye"
  26,118,"Toysa yi-Rabbow yoo kee ken fan meklah mekelaay Ni-fan baxisaay ken bayis, kaadu yoo kee moominiinik yô luk yan mara woo digaalak naggos iyye"
  26,119,Tokkel kaa (Nabii Nuuc kinnuk) kee kaâ luk yan mara kibuk tan doynikil ken naggosne
  26,120,Tohuk lakal kay marak raaqe maray aaminewee maggo leet xuumusne Nabii Nuuc kee kaâ luk suge mara naggosneek gamadal
  26,121,"Diggah too Nabii Nuuc xaaguy taturet kaskassoowa marah astá tan, kaadu keenik ama xaagu yoobbe marak maggo mari keenik yeemene mara makko"
  26,122,Kaadu diggah Nabiyow ku-Rabbi usuk mayso-li xuwaw-li kinni
  26,123,"Qaad deqgsitta kedo sinni farmoyta Huud dirabbosseeh, wohul farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  26,124,"Ken toobokoyti Nabii Huud:Yallak mameesittaanaa? keenik iyye waqdi"
  26,125,Diggah anu siinih amaanat-le farmoyta kinniyo edde rubsumem sin gudduysaamal
  26,126,Toysa Yallak meesitaay yi-amri oggola
  26,127,"Kaadu Yallih farmo sin gudduysaamal galtó sin messera, yi-galtó numul matanaay numul messera ginô Rabbil essera yoo akke waytek iyye"
  26,128,Ummaan aracay fayya iyyal fayya itta qarway dabqah elle gace waytaana digirih xissaanaa
  26,129,"Kaadu maqar-le kalqoota haysittaanaa, addunyal waartaanaah, rabe waytoonu waytaanah innah? (mawaartan rabetton)"
  26,130,Kaadu qidim kee hinnay digaaláh seehadaytu tabbixen waqdi xuwaw kee allaaqal sinni marih xibixih kaa tabbixen
  26,131,Toysa Yallak meesitaay yi-amri oggola
  26,132,Kaadu Yallay maggo afah tan niqmootay taaxigeeni siinih yeceek meesita
  26,133,"Affara xiyyuu (gaalaay, laay, illii kee wadara) kee xaylo siinih yecee (lab-xayloo kee say-xaylo kinnuk)"
  26,134,Kaadu basaatin kee weqta daroori siinih yecee
  26,135,"Nabii Huud: diggah anu kaxxa ayroh (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk) digaalak siinih meesita koroosannuu kee Nabii dirabbossaanamak kate wayteenik keenik iyye"
  26,136,Nel inki gide atu nee kassissam kee hinnay nee kassiisa marih num akke wataamah nanu inkinnah kol manaamina kaak iyye kay mari
  26,137,Ta nanu elle nanim kalah tu hinna nek naharsi marih diinii kee Qaadoodi akke waytek
  26,138,Kaadu nanu abnah naniimil madiggalsimna iyyen
  26,139,"Usun Nabii Huud dirabboyseeniih ken finqisneh, diggah too finqay keenit abnet kaskassoowa marah astá tan, kaadu ama xaagu yoobbe marak maggo mari keenik yeemene mara makko"
  26,140,Kaadu diggah ku-Rabbi usuk mayso-li xuwaw-li kinni
  26,141,"Samuud deqsitta kedó sinni farmoyta Nabii Saalic dirabbosseeh, wohul farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  26,142,Ken toobokoyti Nabii Saalic Yallak mameesittaanaa?keenik iyye waqdi
  26,143,Diggah anu siinih amaanat-le farmoyta kinniyo edde rubsumem sin gudduysaamal
  26,144,Toysa Yallak meesitaay yi-amri oggola
  26,145,"Kaadu Yallih farmo sin gudduysaamal galtó sin messera, yi-galtó numul matanaay numul messera ginô Rabbil essera yoo akke waytek"
  26,146,Sin Rabbi addunyal saayah anuk niqmat addat waarak sin cabaa
  26,147,Basaatin kee weqta daroorih addal
  26,148,"Kaadu buqreeraay, tamiiray (nakilay) tamri kak aleeh xabcinil meesite kal sin cabaa"
  26,149,Kaadu qaleelak qarwa uruttan (orittan) urim teetik naggaarisak batritak dabqah elle gactoonuh
  26,150,Toysa Yallak meesitaay yi-amri oggola
  26,151,Kaadu umaanet caddok tature marih amri moggolina
  26,152,Uma taamat baaxo baysa maray maqaanet baaxo aymaaqewaah amri moggolina
  26,153,"Samuud Nabii Saalicik :cagalah atu elle baaben marih num kinnito kaak iyyen"
  26,154,"Saalicow atu ninnah yan seehadaytu akke waytek kalah tu hinnitok, Nabii kinnitom kok tascasse astá baahey numma yacee marih num tekkek kaak iyyen"
  26,155,"Nabii Saalic keenik iyyeh : ah alaáy yi-asta kinni, is arakta ayrò leeh, isin wonnah timixxige ayroh araki liton"
  26,156,"Kaadu umaaneh tet maxagina, toysa kaxxa ayróh digaalá sin xagelek keenik iyye"
  26,157,"Tokkel arqó teetik kaleeniih tet qideenih, edde luk nadaamite marah maacisen digaala sinnil obtam yismiten waqdi"
  26,158,"Tokkel Nabii Saalic ken kak meesiise digaalá keenil obteeh finqgiteenih, diggah too finqay keenit abnet kaskassoowa marah astá tan, kaadu keenik ama xaagu yoobbe marak maggo mari keenik yeemene mara makko"
  26,159,Kaadu diggah Nabiyow ku-Rabbi usuk mayso-li xuwaw-li kinni
  26,160,"Nabii Luut mari sinni farmoyta Nabii Luut dirabboyseeh, wohul farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  26,161,Ken toobokoyti Nabii Luut Yallak mameesittaanaa ? keenik iyye waqdi
  26,162,Diggah anu siinih amaanat-le farmoyta kinniyo edde rubsumem sin gudduysaamal
  26,163,Toysa Yallak meesitaay yi-amri oggola
  26,164,"Kaadu Yallih farmo sin gudduysaamal galtó sin messera, yi-galtó numul matanaay numul messera ginô Rabbil essera yoo akke waytek iyye"
  26,165,Isin Labhal fidoh orobtaanaa raqqa itta ginok fanaak
  26,166,Kaadu sin Rabbi sin agabuy edde xaltoonuh siinih gine cabtaanaa? Wonna hinnay isin ama uma taamat (labhal orbaanam kinnuk) caddok tatra mara kinniton keenik iyye
  26,167,"Nabii Luut mari:luutow labhal fidoh orobnaamak nee wassaamak kate waytek, diggaluk baaxok yeyyeqsimeeh xiiriyen marih num akketto kaak iyyen"
  26,168,"Nabii Luut keenil gacisak:diggah anu isin abtan uma taama kaxxa naqabuh niqba marih num kinniyo keenik iyye"
  26,169,"Nabii Luut isi Rabbi kallacak:yi- Rabbow yoo kee yi-buxah marak yol teemeneemiiy keenik kalah yol yeemene mara, yi-mari aba uma taamaa kee keenil obtu wayta digaalák nee naggos iyye"
  26,170,Tokkel kaa kee kay buxah maraay kaal teemenem inkih naggosneh
  26,171,Idaltô daaqaynah umeynay (Nabii luut barra kinnuk) digaalát raaqe maray finqitê luk raqteeh finqitte akke waytek koroositteemih sabbatah
  26,172,Tohuk lakat aka mara (Nabii luut mara kinnuk) bayisneh
  26,173,"Kaadu qaraanak xeet keenil oobisne digaaláh robti innah, tokkel Yallih farmoyti Nabii Luut meesiise maral robti innah obte digaalá manxu qaxumaah"
  26,174,"Diggah too Nabii Luut marat tekke digaalat kaskassoowa marah astá tan, kaadu keenik maggo mari yeemene mara makko"
  26,175,Kaadu diggah Nabiyow ku-Rabbi usuk mayso-li xuwaw-li kinni
  26,176,"Garbô mari sinni farmoyta Nabii Shuqeybi dirabboyseeh, wohul Yallih farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken"
  26,177,Nabii Shuqeybi Yallak mameesittaanaa?keenik iyye waqdi
  26,178,Diggah anu siinih amaanat-le farmoyta kinniyo edde rubsume diini sin gudduysaamal
  26,179,Toysa Yallak meesitaay yi-amri oggola keenik iyye
  26,180,"Kaadu Yallih farmo sin gudduysaamal galtó sin messera, yi-galtó numul matanaay numul messera ginô Rabbil essera yoo akke waytek"